    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece bugs together to form your attacks in this creature collector RPG with the perfect mix of puzzle and strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/f285fb79f677d415c4e302112fd2fb06.poster.avif?t=1757338815\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/f285fb79f677d415c4e302112fd2fb06.webm?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/f285fb79f677d415c4e302112fd2fb06.mp4?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WHAT IS AN INSECTILE?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a cluster of tiles comes together into the shape of a cute bug, that’s called an Insectile! When puzzled together, Insectiles can form into the perfect attack. Collect bugs, build up your party, and form new attacks to collect more bugs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4b591c0b3fe771d95597f3afedbe2cbd.poster.avif?t=1757338815\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4b591c0b3fe771d95597f3afedbe2cbd.webm?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4b591c0b3fe771d95597f3afedbe2cbd.mp4?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STRATEGIZE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assembling the perfect party of Insectiles is about much more than just shape! Synergize unique effects to give your attacks extra oomph! Insectiles can bust shields, counter lethal attacks, sweep damage across entire rows, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4fa26944b83dd11b5b7ae635694a661c.poster.avif?t=1757338815\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4fa26944b83dd11b5b7ae635694a661c.webm?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/4fa26944b83dd11b5b7ae635694a661c.mp4?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAKE NEW FRIENDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loma, the world’s leading Insectile researcher, has found herself trapped in a new form by the effects of a mysterious Insectile! It falls on you to save her. Along the way, you will repair the relationship between the Insectiles and the mushroom people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/c5e25fdc5fd9c93bc7e90aeb63cc952a.poster.avif?t=1757338815\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/c5e25fdc5fd9c93bc7e90aeb63cc952a.webm?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/c5e25fdc5fd9c93bc7e90aeb63cc952a.mp4?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a giant garden in search of every mushroom and Insectile alike! The world of Insectile is lovingly packed with side quests, dangerous bosses, secrets to uncover, and of course, a new Insectile at every turn!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/5355c676a781f0048d56d814aebb4b2f.poster.avif?t=1757338815\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/5355c676a781f0048d56d814aebb4b2f.webm?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045270/extras/5355c676a781f0048d56d814aebb4b2f.mp4?t=1757338815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An innovative and thought-provoking battle system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Insectiles to collect</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An overly confident and obnoxious rival character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wear your favorite Insectiles on your head</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bestiary to fill up with research</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Morph Insectiles into new forms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of grubs</p></li></ul>",
